die and Oliver scurried through the maze of fiery rocks, narrowly dodging molten lava.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eThe provided portion of the document does not contain any information about the name of the lion.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eThere is no mention of a lion in the provided portion of the document.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eThere is no mention of a lion's name in the provided portion of the document.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n=========\nFINAL ANSWER:"}]}HTTP/2.0 200 OK
